title: Did Maryland issue a warning from the Bellburg painting about the attempts to assassinate Donald Trump?
subtitle: A viral image shows a real mark on the side of the road near Hunting Town in Calvert County, which warns the "liberals" to arm themselves.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: A sign in Calvert County, Maryland, held in May 2018, warned the "liberals" to arm themselves in case of attempts to accuse President Donald Trump.
